or P and P, at the Library of Congress.

00:01:34.620 --> 00:01:37.970
Being a reference librarian in
P and P means my job focuses

00:01:37.970 --> 00:01:41.370 position:73%
on connecting researchers and visual materials.

00:01:41.370 --> 00:01:45.830 position:66%
I do that work in person in the Prints and
Photographs Reading Room, over the phone,

00:01:45.830 --> 00:01:47.900 position:73%
