00:01:47.900 --> 00:01:53.260 position:66%
And today Tom and I will be connecting you
with visual materials with a focus on how

00:01:53.260 --> 00:01:56.700
to explore photos and the
stories around them as well

00:01:56.700 --> 00:01:59.950
as make them a part of your
classroom experience.

00:01:59.950 --> 00:02:03.900 position:58%
